                            <comment id="428235" author="adilger" created="Tue, 17 Sep 2024 01:03:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patrick, this patch disabled sanity test_119i by adding it to the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list.  However, that is normally only used for issues that are temporary, and the ticket is left open/unresolved to track that failure until it is fixed.  In this case, however, it seems like that functionality may never be implemented.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Either the subtest (and &quot;&lt;tt&gt;always_except &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18032&quot; title=&quot;disable unaligned AIO&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18032&quot;&gt;LU-18032&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; line) should be removed completely (on the assumption that it will never be fixed), or this ticket should be reopened and removed from the 2.16.0 tracking until this issue is fixed permanently.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
